column1: # CryptoRun Data Layers v1.0 - Provenance Sample
# Purpose: Demonstrates mixed-tier data provenance tracking with Hot/Warm/Cold sources
# freshness_ms: Age of data in milliseconds
# cache_hit: Whether data came from cache (true/false)
# fallback_chain: Comma-separated list of fallback attempts
# data_sample: Sample of actual data retrieved
